title: Season 2, Episode 3: Trumpian Foreign Policy
itunes:author: Charles Kupchan, Emmanuelle Blanc, Chris Gilson, Denise Baron
description: Contributor(s): Charles Kupchan, Emmanuelle Blanc, Chris Gilson, Denise Baron | This episode, we're taking a look at how President Trump's prioritisation of "America First" will impact foreign policy. What will America's presence and actions in the world look like during the Trump era?
